quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  32,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim"
  32,2,"Jippineede Deftere nden, sikke woo alaa e mu'un, ko immorde ka JeyЙ—o winndere nden"
  32,3,"Walla Й“e wi'ay kanko (Muhammadu) o fefindi nde? Si ko woni, ko nde goongaare, immorde ka Joomi maa, fii yo a jertin yimЙ“e, Й“e jertinoowo araano e mun ado maaЙ—a, belajo'o, Й“e feeway"
  32,4,"Ko Alla woni taguЙ—o kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, e nder balЙ—e jeegoo. Refti O fotondiri ka dow \"Arski\". Alanaa on gaanin Makko, giЙ—o wanaa tefoowo. E on waajitotaako? @Corrected"
  32,5,"Himo fewja fiyaakuuji Й—in ka kammu haa ka leydi, refti Й—i Жҙeenga ka Makko, e Гұalaande nde emmbere mun woni, duuЙ“i ujunere e ko limoton"
  32,6,"On [fewjoowo fii Й—um on], ko AnnduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, FooluЙ—o, HinnotooЙ—o"
  32,7,On labinЙ—o kala huunde nde O tagi. O fuЙ—Й—i tagude neЙ—Й—anke ndin e loopal
  32,8,"refti O waЙ—i geyngol makko ngol, e sortondiral, immorde ndihal [maniiyu] lo'uЙ—am"
  32,9,"refi O fotndindiri mo, O wutti e makko Ruuhu Makko on. O waЙ—ani on nanЙ—e, e giiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e. [Kono] fanЙ—ii ko yettonton"
  32,10,"ЖҒe wi': \"E nee, si min majjii ka leydi, eyoo men wontay e tagu hesu?\" Ko woni kamЙ“e e hawrugol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e yedduЙ“e [Й—um]"
  32,11,"Maaku: \"Ko hunnata on, ko malaa'ikaajo maayde on wakkilaaЙ—o on. Refti ko ka Joomi mon rutteteЙ—on"
  32,12,"Sinno a yi'ayno, tuma nde bomЙ“e Й“en ugginta ko'e-maЙ“Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e! [lЖҒe wi'a]: \"Joomi amen, men yi'ii men nanii, rutton men, men golla ko moЖҙЖҙi; menen men yananaama"
  32,13,"Sinno Men muuyuno, Men okkayno kala wonkii peewal makki. Ko woni tun, konngol jojjii immorde e An : \"Ma Mi hebbiniray Jahannama on jinna e yimЙ“e, Й“e denndaangal"
  32,14,"MeeЙ—iree (lepte Й—en) sabu welsindagol mon hawrugol e ndee Гұalaande mon Й—oo. Menen (kadi) Men yejjitii on. MeeЙ—iree lepte luttal, sabu ko huuwaynoЙ—on kon"
  32,15,"Anndee ko gomЙ—inta Aayeeje Amen Й—en, ko Й“en tawЙ“e si Й“e waajoraama Й—e, Й“e suuyiray sujjugol, Й“e subbuhinora yettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, kamЙ“e Й“e townitotaako"
  32,16,"Becce maЙ“Й“e Й—en hino woЙ—Й—itoo e lelorЙ—e Й—en, hiЙ“e noddira Joomi maЙ“Й“e kulol e tama'u; e kon ko Men arsiki Й“e, hiЙ“e wintoo"
  32,17,"Wonkii (woo) anndaa ko maranaa Й“e e ko Й“uЙ“Й“inta Й“ernde, Й—um ko njoЙ“di ko Й“e gollaynoo kon"
  32,18,"E on laatiiЙ—o gomЙ—inЙ—o wa'ay wa on faasiqe? (aa'aa), Й“e fotataa"
  32,19,"Si ko Й“en omЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji weerde jipporde, sabu koЙ“e gollaynoo kon"
  32,20,"Si tawii non ko Й“e faasiqiiЙ“e, haray femporde Й“en Й—on nden, ko ka Yiite: Tuma kala Й“e faalaa yaltugol e magge, Й“e ruttitee e magge, Й“e wi'anee: \"MeeЙ—ee lepte Yiite nge fennayoЙ—on ngen"
  32,21,"Ma Men meeЙ—inir Й“e lepte aduna, ado lepte mawЙ—e Й—en (laakara), belajo'o, Й“e ruttitoto"
  32,22,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұude wano waajoraaЙ—o Aayeeje Joomi mun Й—en, refti o Й—uurnii Й—e ! Pellet, Menen, ko Men yoftotooЙ“e e bomЙ“e Й“en"
  32,23,"GomЙ—ii Men okkii Muusaa Deftere nden, - wata a wonu e sikke e fii hawroygol e makko -, Men waЙ—i nde Й—oworde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“en"
  32,24,"Men waЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e ardiiЙ“e, Й—owirooЙ“e (yimЙ“e Й“en) yamiroore Amen, nde Й“e muГұГұinoo, Й“e woni yananaaЙ“e e Aayeeje Amen Й—en"
  32,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa, ko Kanko senndoyta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Г‘alnde Darngal, e kon ko Й“e lurraynoo e fii mun"
  32,26,"E feeГұanaali Й“e, no foti Й—uuЙ—ude e ko Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e e gire, hiЙ“e yaha e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e? Pellet, no e Й—um, tasakuyeeji ! E Й“ee haqqiltaa"
  32,27,"E Й“e yi'aali, wonnde MeЙ—en soggira ndiyam Й—am ka leydi hokkundi, Men yaltinira Й—am remuru, ndu neemoraaЙ—i maЙ“Й“e e kamЙ“e Гұaamata e mun? E Й“e yi'ataa"
  32,28,"HiЙ“e wi'a: \"Ko honnde tuma woni ngal uddital, si on laatike goonguЙ“e"
  32,29,"Maaku: \"Г‘alnde uddial ngal, ko heeferЙ“e Й“en gomЙ—inoyta nafoytaaЙ“e, wanaa kamЙ“e woni nennanteeЙ“e"
  32,30,"ЖҠuurno Й“e, haЙ“Й“ito-Й—aa. KamЙ“e kan, ko Й“e haЙ“Й“itiiЙ“e (lepte)"